Class Checking

  • java.lang.Object
    • project2adv.Account
      • project2adv.Checking
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    AccountInfo, TransactionHandler

    public class Checking
extends Account
implements AccountInfo
    The Checking class represents a checking account. It extends the Account class and implements the AccountInfo interface to provide specific behavior and details for checking accounts, such as displaying account information and returning the account type.

    This class includes methods to display account details and retrieve the type of account as "Checking". It leverages the functionality defined in the Account superclass.

    See Also:
